WEBVTT

05:59.916 --> 06:00.750
Are you good?

06:00.833 --> 06:01.750
Everything is good.

06:02.041 --> 06:02.875
Who is this?

06:04.791 --> 06:05.958
Wasn't Leo your cousin?

06:37.082 --> 06:38.250
Put them in the case.

06:39.207 --> 06:41.707
Come round the back,
I want to have a word.

08:23.041 --> 08:24.500
Today is different.

08:25.625 --> 08:27.625
This isn't your usual run.

08:29.207 --> 08:31.832
You're going to transport
two sets of diamonds.

08:34.250 --> 08:35.165
Come closer.

08:41.957 --> 08:43.832
Total value, 3 million dollars.

08:44.375 --> 08:45.665
What about the ones in the briefcase?

08:46.040 --> 08:47.333
They're fake.

08:49.540 --> 08:51.665
You need to tie this to your leg.

08:53.915 --> 08:55.958
And don't tell your cousin.

09:12.875 --> 09:13.791
Walk.

09:14.750 --> 09:15.625
Yeah it's fine.

09:19.916 --> 09:21.750
See that car across the street?

09:22.291 --> 09:24.708
He's gonna follow you to Houghtons.
